title: VA - Future Trance Vol. 69 (2014)-OutpostX9
description: Hi guys! Here is Future Trance Vol. 69 along with my final version of CD 3 mixed into one MP3. Please ignore those other dead ones I made some mistakes and I'm upset about them. This is final and ready to burn to a blank CD. Please seed and enjoy. I made CD 3 one mp3 for those of you who enjoy the "VOiCE" style. I did the best I could blending them together as some songs were cut rough.
